      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-cos-rif-dtb      .
           move      01                   to   w-det-cos-rif-tpm      .
           move      srt-num-pro          to   w-det-cos-rif-cnm      .
           perform   det-cos-rif-000      thru det-cos-rif-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
