                     srt-prz-net          =    zero
                     go to prn-liv-det-350.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione coefficiente di cam- *
      *                          * bio attuale per legame valutario    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "CC"                 to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-ope      .
           move      srt-sgl-vpl          to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-sdv      .
           move      srt-tdc-vpl          to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-tdc      .
           move      "DT"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-dat                to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-drc      .
           move      00                   to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-quc      .
           perform   coe-cmb-vlt-cll-000  thru coe-cmb-vlt-cll-999    .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su esito determinazione        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-coe-cmb-vlt-ope    not  = "CC"
                     go to prn-liv-det-350.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione prezzo sottoposto a  *
      *                          * legame valutario                    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      srt-prz-net          to   w-lvl-prz-prz          .
           move      srt-sgl-vpl          to   w-lvl-prz-vlt          .
           move      srt-tdc-vpl          to   w-lvl-prz-tdc          .
           move      srt-ccr-vpl          to   w-lvl-prz-ccr          .
           move      w-coe-cmb-vlt-cdc    to   w-lvl-prz-cdc          .
           move      srt-plm-vpl          to   w-lvl-prz-plm          .
           move      srt-tlm-vpl          to   w-lvl-prz-tlm          .
           perform   lvl-prz-det-000      thru lvl-prz-det-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Spostamento in area di comodo con   *
      *                          * 2 decimali per il prezzo            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-lvl-prz-prz        to   w-det-mrg-lrd-9v2      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Eventuale trattamento decimali      *
      *                          * prezzo per la vendita               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        srt-dec-prz          =    1
                     divide 10            into w-det-mrg-lrd-9v2
           else if   srt-dec-prz          =    2
                     divide 100           into w-det-mrg-lrd-9v2      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Spostamento in area di comodo con   *
      *                          * 4 decimali per il costo             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-cos-rif-cdr    to   w-det-mrg-lrd-9v1      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Eventuale trattamento decimali      *
      *                          * prezzo per costo riferimento        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-cos-rif-dec    =    1
                     divide 10            into w-det-mrg-lrd-9v1
           else if   w-det-cos-rif-dec    =    2
                     divide 100           into w-det-mrg-lrd-9v1      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Eventuale trattamento decimali      *
      *                          * valuta per costo riferimento        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-cos-rif-svc    =    c-sgl
                     go to prn-liv-det-320.
           if        w-det-cos-rif-dvc    =    1
                     divide 10            into w-det-mrg-lrd-9v1
           else if   w-det-cos-rif-dvc    =    2
                     divide 100           into w-det-mrg-lrd-9v1      .
       prn-liv-det-320.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione valore scostamento   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-det-mrg-lrd-9v1    from w-det-mrg-lrd-9v2
                                        giving w-det-mrg-lrd-vsc      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione percentuale scosta-  *
      *                          * mento                               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           multiply  100                  by   w-det-mrg-lrd-vsc      .
           divide    w-det-mrg-lrd-9v2    into w-det-mrg-lrd-vsc
                                        giving w-det-mrg-lrd-pmr
                                               rounded                .
